quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,"Mi woo…óndarii jemma si mbo arii e ni…ď…ďidde."
  92,2,"Mi woo…óndirii √Īalawma sombo hu√Īciima."
  92,3,"Mi woo…óndirii ko o tagi ko gorel e deyel."
  92,4,"Pellet golle mon he…óe ceerti."
  92,5,"Si tawi ko oon tottir…óo o reenti."
  92,6,"O gooŇč…óini baraaji golle mum."
  92,7,"Ma min newnan mo kala jam e newaare."
  92,8,"Si tawi ko oon ngammbu…óo o yondinii."
  92,9,"O yeddi njo…ďdi.(aljanna)."
  92,10,"Ma min newnan …óum sa…óteende."
  92,11,"Nafataa …óum jawdi makko si o saami e yiite."
  92,12,"Ko e amen peewal woni."
  92,13,"Ko minen woodani nguurndam La'akara yo aduna."
  92,14,"Njeertin mi on jayngol hu…ď…ďoowol."
  92,15,"Naatataange si wona …ďur…óo hiite."
  92,16,"OOn jeddu…óo …óuurnii."
  92,17,"Ma wo…ó…óita ngol …ďur…óo reentaade oon woni Abu Bakri yo weluyo Alla won e makko."
  92,18,"OOn tottiroowo jawdi mum ngam o laa…ďa."
  92,19,"Alana hay go'oto ka makko neemo jo…ďetee…óo."
  92,20,"Tawi wona …óa…ď…ďude Alla …ďur…óo toowde O."
  92,21,"Mi woo…óndirii ma o wele."
